6
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:38,240
[SPEAKER_00] Uđimo u emisiju.

7
00:00:40,079 --> 00:00:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pozdrav, ja sam vaš domaćin David Barnard, a danas sam ovdje s Jacobom Eitingom, izvršnim direktorom RevenueCata.

8
00:00:46,159 --> 00:00:57,039
