22
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,680
[SPEAKER_02] Ne znam ni.

23
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,959
[SPEAKER_02] A ona je rekla: O, obrijala si se.

24
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,079
