38
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:54,639
[SPEAKER_01] pet tisuća popisa i shvatili smo da sada imamo posao.

39
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,520
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo ga imali.

40
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:58,960
